Are you trying to lose weight? Then Huntyyyyy you have to try this 16 minute Tabata workout I did today 🏋🏽‍♀️ 

Tabata is a high intensity style of training consisting of going hard with an exercise for 20 seconds followed by a 10 second break. This cycle is repeated 8 times resulting in a 4 minute workout. I went hard with 4 exercises and I am sore bruh! Tabata wore me out but it’s a great way to burn calories, build muscle, and of course lose weight 💃🏾 Do it bc baby summer is around the corner!!!
Active set: @leisureforever 

16 minute Tabata Workout 

4 exercises 
Jumping Jacks (20 seconds on 10 seconds off x 8)

Rest 1 minute 

Mountain Climbers (20 seconds on 10 seconds off x 8)

Rest 1 minute 

Bicycle Curls (20 seconds on 10 seconds off x 8)

Rest 1 minute 

High Knees (20 seconds on 10 seconds off x 8)

Done 💅

Tabata workout for Beginners 

Jumping Jacks (20 seconds on 10 seconds off x 8)

Rest 

High Knees (20 seconds on 10 seconds off x 8)

Done 💅
